      "description": "ValidationResult comparing CFD-predicted hemolysis index to experimental measurements from the FDA generic centrifugal pump test campaign. Simulation-to-experiment agreement assessed across 5 flow-speed operating points. The ValidationResult was produced under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which preceded the released solver build by a single patch revision. The configuration team judged the rc2 and release builds to be effectively the same build, as the only change in the release was a minor floating-point rounding correction in the pressure-velocity coupling loop that was not expected to affect hemolysis QoI. No re-run of the validation suite was performed under the released build; the rc2 results were carried forward as supporting evidence for the released model of record.",
