      "rationale": "FDA generic pump geometry is a reasonable analogue but is not the actual VAD impeller geometry. Operating envelope overlaps 3 of 5 COU operating points. Blood analogue (bovine blood) introduces species-level uncertainty relative to human blood rheology. Achieved level 3; significant extrapolation remains to the Class III VAD COU."
